text: Alexandra Panova and Laura Thorpe were the defending champions, but both players chose not to participate. Oksana Kalashnikova and Danka Kovinić won the title, defeating Irina Ramialison and Constance Sibille in the final, 2–6, 6–3, [10–6]. == Seeds == == Draw == == References == * Draw Lorraine Open 88 - Doubles
